nsferState</a></code> 将状态从服务器传输到客户端。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/platform-server/ServerTransferStateModule#description\">查看更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n<section class=\"deprecated\">\n  <p><strong>已弃用:</strong> no longer needed, you can inject the <code><a href=\"api/core/TransferState\" class=\"code-anchor\">TransferState</a></code> in an app without providing\nthis module.</p>\n\n</section>\n  <section class=\"ngmodule-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\nclass <a href=\"api/platform-server/ServerTransferStateModule\" class=\"code-anchor\">ServerTransferStateModule</a> {\n}\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/platform-server/ServerTransferStateModule#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"btnpstnskyq109d4l05urcld3\">注意：如果使用了 <code><a href=\"api/platform-server/renderApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">renderApplication</a></code> 函数，则不需要此模块。<code><a href=\"api/platform-server/renderApplication\" class=\"code-anchor\">renderApplication</a></code> 使此模块中的所有提供者在应用程序中可用。</p>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core/TransferState\n - api/platform-browser/TransferState\n - api/platform-server\n - guide/deprecations\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core/TransferState\n - api/platform-server\n - api/platform-server/ServerTransferStateModule#description\n - api/platform-server/ServerTransferStateModule#servertransferstatemodule\n - api/platform-server/renderApplication\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/platform-server/src/transfer_state.ts#L44-L58\n-->"}